                                          Components List

Microcontroller  - Arduino Uno

Sensors
    •	Five IR Sensors - To detect the black line on the arena
    •	Two IR Sensors - To detect obstacles in its path

Communication and Power Module
    •	Motor drive (L298N) - To control the DC motors
    •	Three 3.7V Rechargeable Li-ion Batteries

Actuators
    •	Two DC Motors - To provide movement by controlling the wheels
    •	Two Servo Motors - To control the robot's gripper
    •	Gripper - Pick and Place mechanism
